-- Endurance Hires ILS Capital’s Faure as Global Reinsurance Chief
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-02-20T13:40:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-20/endurance-hires-ils-capital-s-faure-as-global-reinsurance-chief.html
Endurance Specialty Holdings Ltd.,
the Bermuda-based provider of property and casualty insurance,
named  Jerome Faure  as chief executive officer of the company’s
global reinsurance unit.  Faure, who starts on March 11, will be responsible for
Endurance’s North America, Bermuda and international reinsurance
operations, the insurer said today in a statement distributed by
Business Wire. Faure worked most recently at ILS Capital
Management in Bermuda.  To contact the reporter on this story:
